{"tid":674661,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"[認真]點解香港居民唔用得國際牌喺香港渣車?","createTime":"2018-05-23T01:37:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-26T06:05:29.000Z","uid":68756,"like":27,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"57d1bc2043f82dd70d15e4f0b0c863a1dbbf9d5c","tid":674661,"uid":68756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T01:37:31.000Z","msg":"前日因為跌咗銀包,唔見曬所有證件。<br />\n去警局報失時,因為工作關係,順便問埋補領駕駛執照之前可否拎住國際駕駛許可證先代替。<br />\n報案室嗰差佬聽到都唔肯定,入一入去問吓上司。<br />\n最後回覆唔得。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁基於好奇心我就問咗幾樣嘢:<br />\n①\t既然PASSPORT可以暫時代替身分證,點解國際駕駛許可證唔可以?<br />\n②\t海外人士就可以用國際駕駛許可證係香港渣,但香港居民就唔得?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n③\t國際駕駛許可證都係運輸處批&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n當然同過差佬交過手都知,啊SIR定規則唔洗你教!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n解嚟解去只係話因為你係香港居民&hellip;&hellip;..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我都無同佢哋理論。<br />\n背景身家清白,無能力改變啲咩。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能政府真係有原因,但作為小市民既我諗咗成日都覺得off到不能理解。"},{"pid":"2c6052683081fde494eb6b22349499e03ca7ed78","tid":674661,"uid":16061,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T02:11:30.000Z","msg":"因為你會留港多過12個月？"},{"pid":"5c82fb76ae050163664a0f33db78da41ba5679fe","tid":674661,"uid":21629,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T02:15:41.000Z","msg":"唔俾係正常 真係有呢條條例<br />\n唔係淨係香港係咁 美國都係咁如果你有當地車牌就唔可以用國際牌代替車牌"},{"pid":"c53a4e253afd1daa4865584343394b01ed44717b","tid":674661,"uid":13343,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T02:25:56.000Z","msg":"好多地方都係咁<br />\n澳洲如果你喺當地住多過一段時間 就唔畀你用非當地牌揸<br />\n<br />\n會當你個國際牌廢咗"},{"pid":"9cf05a87e37b4783b33e6bd70ecde1207fd87057","tid":674661,"uid":19851,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T02:35:41.000Z","msg":"個牌屬於臨時性，長期住就當你resident,要考local 牌<br />\n好多地方都係咁"},{"pid":"4f024fe1ad61d190bd0c301ba7b511197faa0e76","tid":674661,"uid":13343,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"c53a4e253afd1daa4865584343394b01ed44717b","tid":674661,"uid":13343,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T02:25:56.000Z","msg":"好多地方都係咁<br />\n澳洲如果你喺當地住多過一段時間 就唔畀你用非當地牌揸<br />\n<br />\n會當你個國際牌廢咗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T02:36:43.000Z","msg":"If you're a resident of Australia rather than a visitor, you're able to drive in NSW on an overseas licence for 3 months. Within this 3 month period however, you'll need to visit a service centre and transfer your overseas licence to a NSW driver licence.<br />\n<br />\nYou may need to pass a knowledge or driving test, depending on where your overseas licence was issued."},{"pid":"cf447b1c76353ffa7a047d4194c8e617a2159a43","tid":674661,"uid":45952,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T02:38:59.000Z","msg":"其實香港居民用外國passport 入境加當地簽發國際牌都可以用<br />\n<br />\n但無人會咁得閒咁玩，反正你有外國牌多數運輸署會免試比個香港牌你"},{"pid":"dd560a09ea1c4acc0b6fba393d92ac42b2d612f4","tid":674661,"uid":28418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T02:46:30.000Z","msg":"用過 冇事"},{"pid":"42cde5d246b743d43f097a1feb558734d4473d6a","tid":674661,"uid":33652,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T03:09:33.000Z","msg":"一般汽車保險唔受國際牌"},{"pid":"37d8e3d25906dc8a3affdf2904e91f45a417c88c","tid":674661,"uid":9230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42cde5d246b743d43f097a1feb558734d4473d6a","tid":674661,"uid":33652,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T03:09:33.000Z","msg":"一般汽車保險唔受國際牌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T05:36:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44319d9f2c2495b25a6dd1bed5f1175fb208b6bb","tid":674661,"uid":66242,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T05:58:53.000Z","msg":"樓主係問點解<br />\n一個二個答人哋外國都係咁<br />\n而家啲人邏輯思維弱到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cb8e3226a3380164068569c9aa4c46d6d1918b4","tid":674661,"uid":14625,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T11:51:49.000Z","msg":"因為國際車牌唔係真係車牌 佢真名係國際駕駛許可證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢只係證明你個車牌簽發地係受日內瓦公約認可<br />\n行街紙都唔可以代替身份證啦ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cad8b7154d06dd541492f230e41a4d090de0699d","tid":674661,"uid":84116,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T18:05:58.000Z","msg":"因為國際牌要連埋你本身個車牌<span style=\"color: red;\">一齊</span>用先有效，如果唔連埋一齊用，個國際牌等於廢紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40ce94b95bff6122efa338711e83a8cb2cd5c531","tid":674661,"uid":105166,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T18:11:54.000Z","msg":"我想問咁用唔用得美國牌係香港揸車㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"735eefc1ce11a484b8cada1e5a73aa952367b8cb","tid":674661,"uid":105166,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"cad8b7154d06dd541492f230e41a4d090de0699d","tid":674661,"uid":84116,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T18:05:58.000Z","msg":"因為國際牌要連埋你本身個車牌<span style=\"color: red;\">一齊</span>用先有效，如果唔連埋一齊用，個國際牌等於廢紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T18:12:10.000Z","msg":"正解"},{"pid":"b84ac9c3a697be617124feabe024013955e0bc8a","tid":674661,"uid":131241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf447b1c76353ffa7a047d4194c8e617a2159a43","tid":674661,"uid":45952,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T02:38:59.000Z","msg":"其實香港居民用外國passport 入境加當地簽發國際牌都可以用<br />\n<br />\n但無人會咁得閒咁玩，反正你有外國牌多數運輸署會免試比個香港牌你"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T18:13:49.000Z","msg":"香港好多有錢佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\